OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy initially but
OL,6,Fsoon brightening up from the south.
OL,7,FBecoming warm in the afternoon,
OL,8,Fparticularly in the south, where there
OL,9,Fmay be some brief sunny spells.
OL,10,FBreezy, especially near coasts and
OL,11,Fhills.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIncreasingly cloudy through
OL,14,Fthe evening and overnight, with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of light rain possible
OL,16,Fduring the early hours. Breezy,
OL,17,Fespecially near coasts and hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
