OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA largely cloudy start,
OL,6,Fespecially across western hills.
OL,7,FTurning bright, with some sunny spells
OL,8,Flater in the day. Winds easing. Warm.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,11,Fand sunny to end the week. Light
OL,12,Fwinds, though breezier across hills
OL,13,Fand for most on Friday. Temperatures
OL,14,Fincreasing, becoming very warm or hot.
